{"tid":1060471,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(估計爛尾)直播不負責任單拖歐洲遊記","createTime":"2019-03-13T19:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T14:53:52.000Z","uid":96525,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"df28f0fb024f9f495429d7190ad54bb85b3fe349","tid":1060471,"uid":96525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T19:40:32.000Z","msg":"而家喺西維爾休息緊，悶悶地直播我呢幾日做過啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講明先我做事有頭無尾，個post好大機會爛尾0參考價值純粹分享<br />\n嗰啲咩著名景點我大部分都無去，完全係hea住咁旅行<br />\n<br />\n一直都好想試下去歐洲，但身邊嘅朋友都0興趣，然後就揀咗3月淡季出發第一次自己去旅行<br />\n以前去旅行都係喺亞洲地區，而且次次都有人同行，平時我連喺香港都會經常盪失路，而家完全無心理準備之下就去咗巴塞隆拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾乎無plan過行程，所以我啲朋友都已經有定幫我開追悼會嘅準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個個都話我會比人偷呃拐搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次搭嘅airline係惡名遠播嘅British Airway，仲要係當日買，因為我睇錯時間miss咗班機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以就遲咗一日出發<br />\n點解BA惡名遠播，上網睇啲人話因為個機場太大太混亂，係全球最繁忙嘅機場之一<br />\n咁我就係搭夜晚11點半夜機，喺London Heathrow轉機去巴塞隆拿<br />\n去倫敦嗰程機要搭成13個鐘，第一次坐長途機又無想像中咁痛苦，睇咗兩三套戲，食咗兩餐，其餘時間都喺度訓，雖然啲位好窄下但我又訓得算冧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能我本身不受地域環境限制都可以訓得著<br />\n<br />\n戰績：曾經喺西鐵企喺度挨住嘢訓著，喺靈堂摺摺下元寶訓著，喺泰國坐篤篤車熟睡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q9tPN3V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ9tPN3V.png&h=49bf2700&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一餐係雞排長通粉，右下角個雞胸薏米沙津難食到痴線，成世人都未食過咁難食嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有個朱古力蛋糕配覆盆子果醬甜到嘔，食咗兩口就放棄<br />\n不過個主菜雞排長通粉係入到口的，我有食曬<br />\n其實唔係比個星空仰望派我食嘅話基本上我都無乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知星空仰望派係咩嚟可自行google<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q8XXWX8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ8XXWX8.png&h=f33d8e6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早餐係蛋捲茄汁豆薯仔，食咗半份忍唔住要放棄，好咸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個蛋糕都好硬，食咗少少又放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不個個鮮慘汁又幾好飲<br />\n<br />\n到達倫敦係當地時間4點幾左右，然後就轉機去巴塞隆拿<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Pm2oG4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Pm2oG4.png&h=53bf52e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n落機時係當地時間早上九點，然後就喺機場「TABAC」煙草店買張T10交通卡，巴塞嘅交通我覺得算幾方便，除咗機場巴士，交通卡係地鐵巴士輕鐵都通用，佢只係一張硬卡紙，用咗一次之後會有行字印上去話比你知仲剩返幾多次<br />\nT10即係你可以搭十次車，如果你用唔到十次可以一張T10卡share比你同行嘅人用（即係你入咗閘後，可以遞張卡比你身後同行嘅人用嚟入閘）<br />\n<br />\n首先要喺機場搭巴士出市區先，藍色車身A1，好似係5.5EUR，喺Pl. Espanya - FGC度落車，再轉H16巴士去我住嗰區<br />\n巴士嘅交通卡用法就好似返工打卡咁，咁講大家應該明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/22iTvnV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F22iTvnV.png&h=849dc92c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n落車後喺我住嗰間民宿附近求其搵個地方食早餐，2.95EUR<br />\n<br />\n食完又未夠鐘check in，我住嗰度隔離就係海灘，就去海邊坐住hea下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JaXp0iz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJaXp0iz.png&h=093ed4e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實3月嘅西班牙都好大風同埋有啲凍，得十幾度，不過啲當地人喺海灘又游水又滑浪都玩得好開心下，坐坐下仲見到有個阿婆玩天體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我就凍到震，喺海邊鳩咗陣就返咗去沖涼訓，已經超過24個鐘無訓過落張床度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁就完結咗我第一日"},{"pid":"c412a0903ad9bca786fa45eaa1eb6b785288b1fd","tid":1060471,"uid":96525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T19:41:35.000Z","msg":"<strong>Day2 睇波</strong><br />\n嚟到巴塞，雖然我唔係巴塞fans但點都要去魯營球場睇波嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n場波踢6點半，訓醒喺民宿附近食咗個唔知咩12EUR好似係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HQDgRwv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHQDgRwv.png&h=8749d4bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我估就應該係豬肉嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cPX9r5B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcPX9r5B.png&h=45e76d86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食完又返去hea陣就出發去魯營啦，要轉兩次地鐵，因為佢地唔同線（就當成你喺觀塘線轉將軍澳線再轉港島線咁啦）<br />\n我喺L4線Poblenou站搭6個站，喺Urquinaona落，再轉L1線，搭5個站喺Pl. Espanya落，再轉L3搭6個站喺Palau Reial落車<br />\n喺L1線遇到小插曲，因為啲車站名真係幾難睇，我要攞住部電話同塊站牌對名，呢個時候有個10幾歲左右嘅白人女仔走嚟問我要去邊，咁我就好自然咁比佢睇我要喺Pl. Espanya落，跟住咁啱有車佢就示意呢架車啱㗎喇上啦<br />\n由於嗰日係星期六，所以架車都幾逼下，咁同個白人女仔同行嘅有個拉丁裔女仔，佢就不斷同我講嘢（雖然我聽唔明，後來我先知佢係負責分散我注意力），佢嘅意思話我搭5個站就得<br />\n突然個白人女仔就扮逼成個人壓埋嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />由於個動作實在太突兀，所以我即刻望下個袋，果不其然個扣打開咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁我檢查好銀包電話仲喺度就即刻扣返好，再用手禁住個袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住嗰兩條女就相視講咗啲我聽唔明嘅嘢，然後個拉丁裔女仔繼續同我講啲我聽唔明嘅嘢，做啲我睇唔明嘅手勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個時候我已經唔想理佢，講咗句sorry I don&rsquo;t understand就廢時理佢，順便講多句Gracias（謝謝）叫做象徵式多撚謝佢同我講要5個站落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住佢地見事敗就搭咗一個站就落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>總結：千萬唔好喺西班牙擺出迷惘嘅表情，尤其喺地鐵，如果有人想埋嚟幫你都唔好比佢幫，有兩個人嗰啲都係一個負責分散你注意力，一個負責偷嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小人之心都係咁話</strong><br />\n<br />\n轉到L3線，已經見到有好多疤狗喺車箱內好激情咁唱會歌吹哨子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又攬曬巴塞毛巾，戴巴塞cap帽咁....爭在未fing埋會旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一落車唔駛搵路，跟住人群行就得<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KvGm908.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKvGm908.png&h=0ff7772b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於去到嗰陣都只係4點半，踢6點半仲有大把時間，諗住食口煙仔先<br />\n但....我包煙呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌那星我比條臭雞偷撚咗包煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冚家鏟<br />\n咁我個袋口位都幾窄下，我包煙就放最出，如果要攞入面啲嘢就要攞咗包煙出嚟先，啱啱就係比條女偷咗我包煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />八婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁都無辦法啦，唯有喺附近hea下等入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ayEcea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ayEcea.png&h=e306cfaa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9M1isNx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9M1isNx.png&h=078c481a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sLVSxee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsLVSxee.png&h=c061e999&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔同看台有唔同入口，算幾方便<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DgAnUzU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDgAnUzU.png&h=8da4a76e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n非正式統計有超過七成人都係著美斯波衫"},{"pid":"f5370e4249bda30399a87ba0baa6dfb93edc1324","tid":1060471,"uid":143093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T19:44:06.000Z","msg":"十五妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757cd57846d9ddbeed3b01e3af3a13fbcf672265","tid":1060471,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T19:44:26.000Z","msg":"皮已正"},{"pid":"9d039286a33a66fb7d6be016b5fbc0e61e435673","tid":1060471,"uid":124491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T19:47:44.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"0ace49a29c7e334ece0af17766c5be7ba707ad93","tid":1060471,"uid":96525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5370e4249bda30399a87ba0baa6dfb93edc1324","tid":1060471,"uid":143093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T19:44:06.000Z","msg":"十五妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T19:50:29.000Z","msg":"多謝G持ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f24ea257b4077c5c3008d10c4e78b7aec58cd305","tid":1060471,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T00:27:20.000Z","msg":"有無個袋既相？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c9fb9fa4b890493c4bb0343ccbc3c6eb69ae6f","tid":1060471,"uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T02:48:05.000Z","msg":"好撚好睇"},{"pid":"5659324deed00fc0b4b6601b3c3018ec4d840fd7","tid":1060471,"uid":96525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f24ea257b4077c5c3008d10c4e78b7aec58cd305","tid":1060471,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T00:27:20.000Z","msg":"有無個袋既相？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T12:41:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1yXYyBL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yXYyBL.png&h=9e15f24a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8019b06deb49f69716dbcc322c75dd1a56661a05","tid":1060471,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T14:53:52.000Z","msg":"有update未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}